    Scope and Contents
In addition to all sessions, these records include administrative working papers for the Intersession.  Speakers are: Alex B. Lacy, Richard Hey, Michael Marsden, Jane Howard, Marianne Ferber, Edward Shorter, Joyce Antler, John Demos, Arhtur J. Norton, Alvin Poussaint, Mary Hotvedt, Rae Lesser Blumberg, and Robert Rice.
Topics included contemporary images of families, roles and functions of families, trends and transitions in family structures, alternative family forms, and families and public policy.  
  
